name: ゼーレ - Seele / Honkai: Star Rail - 崩壊スターレイル
description:
N°34 Release, ゼーレ - Seele From Honkai: Star Rail - 崩壊スターレイル.

You can now request a Character's LORA. CLICK HERE

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Click on Show more for Weight & Trigger recommendation, Also click on About This Version at Right Corner for more Info.

Many people requested me Seele on my Poll, & I wanted one too ahah, so there you go i created it, i tryed to be the most precise with the max quality possible atm.

About this Lora:

  • Lora trained on 84+ Images, That i sorted manually, At the Max Quality Possible (Orginal Art 4K + Official Art 4K) SFW+NFSW.

  • Trained at 768x Resolution for maximum Detail & Quality.

  • NAI Used, Work with Majority of the Anime Model's.

  • Flexibility is Ok/Good.

  • Work's greatly with Detail Tweaker Lora. (I Recommend to use it).

  • Can probably do Seele in Realistic Cosplay.

For Prompts & Weight:

About Trigger Words & Prompts: SeeleV4 (For Trigger) & for prompts just refer to examples images & you can put any prompts you want.

Weight recommended: 0.6-1. - Best Result 0.7-1.

Leave a Review & Share you're image in comments if you appreciate this Work :).

modelVersions.name: V4
modelVersions.description:
I pruned Purple hair, Purple eyes, so normally you don't need to put in prompt, but if they don't appear put: ((Purple hair, Purple Eyes)) prompt.

For Official Default Skin: Sometime the best weights is varying per model's, Like 0.7-1.

For Flexibility: for like clothes that don't exist put 0.6 - 0.8 Weight, See my Examples images for this.

Also if you don't want something to appear, put it in Negative Prompt.
